##### 3.3.2 AreaChart

Displays time-series or continuous data as an area chart.

**Component Name:** `"AreaChart"`

**Props:**
| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `title` | `string` | Yes | Chart title |
| `subtitle` | `string` | No | Chart subtitle/description |
| `data_source_id` | `string` | Yes | Reference to data source (array with `x` and `y` fields) |
| `height` | `number` | No | Chart height in pixels (default: 300) |
| `config` | `AreaChartConfig` | Yes | Chart configuration |
| `statistics` | `StatItem[]` | No | Key statistics to display below chart |
| `notes` | `string[]` | No | Notes to display |

**AreaChartConfig Schema:**
```typescript
{
  "xaxis_label": string,     // X-axis label
  "yaxis_label": string,     // Y-axis label
  "fill_color": string,      // Area fill color (hex)
  "stroke_color": string,    // Line stroke color (hex)
  "fill_opacity": number,    // Fill opacity 0-1 (default: 0.4)
  "curve": "smooth" | "linear",  // Line curve type
  "showGrid": boolean        // Show grid lines
}
```

**Data Source Format:** Must return array of objects with `x` and `y`:
```json
[
  { "x": 0, "y": 65 },
  { "x": 3, "y": 58 },
  { "x": 6, "y": 45 }
]
```

**Usage Example:**
```json
{
  "component": "AreaChart",
  "props": {
    "title": "Progression-Free Survival",
    "subtitle": "Months from treatment start",
    "data_source_id": "pfs_data",
    "height": 400,
    "config": {
      "xaxis_label": "Months",
      "yaxis_label": "Patients",
      "fill_color": "#E0E7FF",
      "stroke_color": "#6366F1",
      "fill_opacity": 0.4,
      "curve": "smooth",
      "showGrid": true
    }
  }
}
```

